---
// create variables for age and years of experience
const date = new Date();
const age = date.getFullYear() - 2004;
const experience = date.getFullYear() - 2022;
---
<section class="flex flex-col gap-6 justify-center items-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
  <div
    class="[&>p]:mb-4 [&_*strong]:text-yellow-400 [&_*strong]:font-semibold text-pretty"
  >
    <p>
      I'm Eliseo Francisco Arévalo, a <strong>{ age }-year-old</strong> software developer with
      about <strong>{ experience } years of experience</strong> building web applications.
    </p>

    <p>
      I've worked on projects from interactive maps to onboarding systems in fintechs. 
      What I enjoy most is understanding the complete problem before writing code.
    </p>

    <p>
      I believe the best technical solution isn't always the most complex. I prefer simple 
      systems that work well and other developers can easily understand.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
